    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Prevent Abuse By Using Interstate Exchange Act of 2016 or the Prevent ABUSE Act of 2016</b></p> <p>This bill requires a state that receives a prescription drug monitoring program implementation and enhancement grant to set aside at least 20% of grant funds to facilitate interstate electronic information sharing about prescriptions for controlled substances. </p>]]></text>
